      "cookedHtml": "<p>We’re excited to introduce <strong>Risk Radar</strong> — a lightweight risk management tool designed specifically for <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> teams!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/e/8e34f4b6366581ab1531cc84f64ee187a9813b39.jpeg\" title=\"App gallery images 2\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/e/8e34f4b6366581ab1531cc84f64ee187a9813b39_2_690x345.jpeg\" alt=\"App gallery images 2\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">App gallery images 2</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 174 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/magnifying_glass_tilted_left.png?v=14\" title=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>What it does:</strong><br />\nQuickly assess the risk level of any item based on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Likelihood of a problem</li>\n<li>Impact on the project</li>\n<li>Difficulty to fix</li>\n</ul>\n<p>It instantly calculates a <strong>risk score</strong> and displays a <strong>color-coded badge</strong> right inside the item — helping your team stay focused and ahead of blockers.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/light_bulb.png?v=14\" title=\":light_bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":light_bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Why use Risk Radar?</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Spot potential issues early<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Prioritize tasks with confidence<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=14\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Make risks transparent and visible to everyone</p>\n<hr />\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/inbox_tray.png?v=14\" title=\":inbox_tray:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":inbox_tray:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Try it now on the <strong><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/10000796\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday marketplace</a></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/movie_camera.png?v=14\" title=\":movie_camera:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":movie_camera:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong><a href=\"https://youtu.be/jPR5n7hTT-I\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Watch Demo</a></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/open_book.png?v=14\" title=\":open_book:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_book:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong><a href=\"https://meltedmensoftware.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RRFM/pages/35160065/Getting+Started+with+Risk+Radar+in+monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Read Documentation</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>We’d love your feedback — feel free to ask questions or suggest improvements below!</p>"
